{"tid":1366121,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"對新界佬來講，乜野可怕過燒村？","createTime":"2019-07-26T01:03:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T15:36:35.000Z","uid":275872,"like":157,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"6f020c40c5717a2c7a36c415f9ca0aa7c9c3674c","tid":1366121,"uid":275872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T01:03:23.000Z","msg":"就係你唔比佢僭建一兩層，等佢唔可以每人間屋無啦啦多一千尺。<br />\n<br />\n就係你唔比佢套丁、屯地，等佢唔可以靠違犯起丁屋，每棟賺7百萬。<br />\n<br />\n就係你唔比佢做棕地，等佢唔可以霸住幾千尺官地，每年賺幾十幾百億。(講緊全新界有1500萬尺棕地呀！)<br />\n<br />\n你做到以上幾樣，整個鄉黑勢力就會瓦解。而家向政府要求嚴正執法，打僭建、套丁、收棕地，香港先有機會回覆正常。<br />\n<br />\n(轉載自書店老闆個人Facebook)"},{"pid":"bca26d6f7453496f7099a520bb094ca96414278f","tid":1366121,"uid":275872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T01:04:19.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"58a25cb9a6ad6fb9655548cb31e3c838f35e1a83","tid":1366121,"uid":275872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T01:05:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92ec20e07cee1b9e11708d17f0ce124ff1e3a728","tid":1366121,"uid":275872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T01:08:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b7854a594aeeb227a8740fc1b92800562e0e562","tid":1366121,"uid":161990,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T01:09:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1iVuvP5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1iVuvP5.gif&h=9bc8a809&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9d6533f8c2e7abcfb4a08511c8aa4e9c66a5383a","tid":1366121,"uid":275872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T01:09:56.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c610ed8d7500fa4e6da240bb741a9ec173bace25","tid":1366121,"uid":273353,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T01:10:03.000Z","msg":"冇丁權<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fa